1
00:00:03,400 --> 00:00:07,996
丹中尉 你来做什么？
Lieutenant Dan, what are you doing here?

2
00:00:08,071 --> 00:00:11,438
嗯 我想到海中施展拳脚
Well, thought I'd try out my sea legs.

3
00:00:11,509 --> 00:00:14,444
可是你没有脚了 丹中尉
Well, you ain't got no legs, Lieutenant Dan.

4
00:00:14,512 --> 00:00:15,945
是的 我知道
Yes, I know that.

5
00:00:16,014 --> 00:00:20,212
你写了封信给我 白痴
You wrote me a letter, you idiot.

6
00:00:20,285 --> 00:00:22,651
好了 福雷斯甘船长
Well, well. Captain Forrest Gump.

7
00:00:22,722 --> 00:00:25,589
我要亲眼来看看…
I had to see this for myself...

8
00:00:26,893 --> 00:00:28,360
并且…
and...

9
00:00:28,429 --> 00:00:32,866
我说过如果你能当捕虾船的船长
I told you if you were ever a shrimp boat captain,

10
00:00:32,933 --> 00:00:34,867
我就来当你的大副
that I'd be your first mate.

11
00:00:34,936 --> 00:00:36,597
所以我来了
Well, here I am.

12
00:00:36,671 --> 00:00:38,605
我是信守诺言的
I'm a man of my word .

13
00:00:38,673 --> 00:00:39,697
好的
O.K.

14
00:00:39,775 --> 00:00:41,936
但你别以为
But don't you be thinking

15
00:00:42,011 --> 00:00:44,445
我会叫你长官
that I'm going to be calling you "sir."

16
00:00:44,513 --> 00:00:45,445
不用 长官
No, sir.

